section.section:
In complying with subsection (b)(1) of this section, the Governor, by executive order, shall designate any employee of an executive unit who is:
a home inspector or licensed home inspector, under § 16-101 of the Business Occupations and Professions Article;
a building code enforcement official employed by the State;
an accredited inspector of lead for the Department of the Environment under § 6-818 of the Environment Article; or
an environmental sanitarian under Title 11 of the Environment Article.
